<idea-plugin>
    <id>ReadOnly File Encoding Panel</id>
    <name>ReadOnly File Encoding Panel</name>
    <vendor email="cqy2016@gmail.com" url="https://github.com/chenqiyue/ReadOnlyFileEncodingPanel">cqy</vendor>

    <description><![CDATA[
    增加一个专门用于修改只读文件编码的status bar，用于修复jar文件无法修改文件编码的问题
    ]]></description>

    <change-notes><![CDATA[
    <ul>
        <li><b>1.0</b> 支持2020.3，持久化只读文件编码到项目配置中</li>
        <li><b>1.1</b> 支持2021.1.1</li>
        <li><b>1.2</b> 支持2022.3</li>
    </ul>
    ]]></change-notes>

    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <statusBarWidgetFactory implementation="com.chenqiyue.idea.bugfix.encoding.ReadOnlyFileEncodingStatusBarWidgetFactory"/>
    </extensions>

    <actions>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>